Package com.mathtastic.controller

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnswerQuestion
    AnswerQuestion handles numbers sent through appleAdditionAskQuestion.jsp.
    AskQuestion
    AskQuestion handles setup for the game logic sent through either the StartGame class or through appleAddition.jsp.
    EndGame
    EndGame handles tracking "tricky questions" and displays game results to appleAdditionResults.jsp.
    SignInUser
    SignInUser signs in an existing user.
    SignOutUser
    SignOutUser removes the user signed in from the current session
    SignUpUser
    SignUpUser adds new users to the database based on their email.
    StartGame
    StartGame handles the tear-down of unfinished games and setup of a new game.
    UpdateUser
    UpdateUser checks the password entered on myAccount.jsp and updates the user.
    ViewTrickyQuestions
    ViewTrickyQuestions gets all of the "tricky questions" from the Apple Addition game in a user's history and displays them on trickyQuestions.jsp.
